      <title>天空新闻称 Blackstone 准备进行新的 Hipgnosis 投标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/blackstone-prepares-to-make-fresh-hipgnosis-bid-sky-news-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据天空新闻报道，Blackstone Inc. 正在敲定收购 Hipgnosis Songs Fund Ltd. 的修订要约，因为这家私募股权公司希望加强对伦敦上市音乐版权投资者的竞购竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/blackstone-prepares-to-make-fresh-hipgnosis-bid-sky-news-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 15:04:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
