      <title>华尔街多头表示，即使不降息，股市反弹也能恢复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/us-stocks-wall-street-bulls-say-rally-can-power-on-even-without-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[即使对美联储今年降息的押注完全被放弃，强劲的全球经济增长也可能为股市提供足够的支撑，以恢复破纪录的涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/us-stocks-wall-street-bulls-say-rally-can-power-on-even-without-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 14:30:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
